## Edge Cases

| Case | Mitigation |
|------|-----------|
| Old `"system"/"dark"` in localStorage | `migrateStoredValue` maps to `"t3-dark"` |
| Old `"light"` in localStorage | Mapped to `"t3-light"` |
| Stale inline styles across theme switches | Every `applyTheme` call overwrites all props; no `removeProperty` needed |
| `color-mix(var(--background) ...)` cascade | CSS custom prop resolution is live; inline `--background` flows into derived vars |
| `noUncheckedIndexedAccess` strict mode | `Record<ThemeId, AppTheme>` index always returns `AppTheme` (not `| undefined`) |
| DiffWorkerPoolProvider | Only reads `resolvedTheme: "light" \| "dark"` — unchanged |

